 Akah Nnani and Wife Claire Odera Nollywood actor Akah Nnani and his wife Claire have welcomed their first child together and they can’t wait to share their birth story with you soon. The couple made the announcement on their joint Instagram page with a cute photo taken few hours before their baby arrived, and captioned it: “2 lovers and a love child ?? Our baby came shortly (literally a few hours) after this photo. It really was the most unforgettable memory ever and we can’t wait to share our birth story with you soon. ? Thank you so much for the love and prayers. We love you!!” View this post on Instagram A post shared by Akah & Claire Nnani (@akahandclaire)